description: Welcome to Trimount Place—South Boston’s newest Luxury Development is designed to inspire and built to last. Nestled in the city's fastest-growing neighborhood, Trimount Place seats you at the intersection of history and progress. Each residence is thoughtfully designed with 5” white oak floors, Calacatta Colorado quartz countertops, and custom shaker cabinetry in a stylish mix of white and light grey. The kitchens boast Samsung appliances, and a La Belle Air ceramic backsplash blending elegance with functionality. Spa-like bathrooms feature polished porcelain shower walls, Bianco Carrara marble mosaic shower floors, and navy or white shaker vanities, creating a serene retreat. Beyond your home, enjoy two breathtaking roof decks, a sky lounge, a state-of-the-art fitness center, a pet spa, community room, and more. Plus, the DEVELOPER IS OFFERING AN INTEREST RATE BUY-DOWN, making luxury living more attainable. Will YOU be moving into Trimount Place in 2025? Schedule your tour today!
